{"tid":2066581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我好憎我家姐","createTime":"2020-06-16T11:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T12:45:23.000Z","uid":194203,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8fdd8336b6f86de253b5f3233c375f26ee38273e","tid":2066581,"uid":194203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:14:28.000Z","msg":"小妹幾年前頂唔順家姐啲閪人性格<br />\n搬咗出去同人夾租<br />\n咁有時我都會同男朋友番屋企食下飯<br />\n不過好多時都係趁佢唔喺屋企先番廢事見<br />\n（佢好撚鍾意對我男朋友同細佬女朋友黑面）<br />\n咁前幾日我就同男朋友番去食飯<br />\n食完傾下計同細佬打下機就留夜咗，咁岩家姐又話唔番，所以兩老就叫我地留低訓<br />\n咁我禮貌上都有講聲，家姐同我以前上下格床既，個晚我地就訓番我張上格床<br />\n第二日我男朋友有野做走咗<br />\n咁我就開電腦煲下劇啦<br />\n點知原來家姐無log out WhatsApp<br />\n然後突然就彈咗通知出黎<br />\n咁我又仆街既我開咗黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知內容就係鬧鳩我同我男朋友<br />\n話我地實喺佢間房搞野 仲話我搬咗出去就咪喺屋企搞 要搞就去開房搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嬲到仆街<br />\n仲要見到佢個fd約佢一陣食元氣我屌佢老味<br />\n點先可以斷絕關係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween，我有留幾套衫喺屋企，個晚我開衣櫃換衫，見到佢買左幾套情趣內衣待用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b8ec52c0cfa86d30c86361077084ab39b6ccc5","tid":2066581,"uid":213978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:16:40.000Z","msg":"介紹黎識幫你教返好佢"},{"pid":"59f03fa71fadbfc3e36821591d9eb481cebae6b9","tid":2066581,"uid":206522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"Web版whatsapp冇佢部電話係度可以開到？"},{"pid":"43961d6900b0e73b15d9e8310b9985b91e0230ec","tid":2066581,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:17:16.000Z","msg":"Gay<br />\n男人先會叫自己小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3c4ab1632b0ce3cc7af1d09448a041bc057ac6","tid":2066581,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:17:57.000Z","msg":"著佢套情趣內衣扑野,再放返入去衣櫃"},{"pid":"2b3f83e10d6ae7b75458a399dac4bb044d820ef4","tid":2066581,"uid":110204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:43:35.000Z","msg":"叫你男朋友馴服下你家姐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7cb7aa020b46e94a182d7e1e0d6650901378e7","tid":2066581,"uid":194203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f03fa71fadbfc3e36821591d9eb481cebae6b9","tid":2066581,"uid":206522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"Web版whatsapp冇佢部電話係度可以開到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"得㗎"},{"pid":"4802bf925744c2c2bbceedf307fb5e4f7f60a400","tid":2066581,"uid":194203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b3f83e10d6ae7b75458a399dac4bb044d820ef4","tid":2066581,"uid":110204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:43:35.000Z","msg":"叫你男朋友馴服下你家姐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T12:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f215d4d2c2f19597d05caea5ade6fb35a7e284","tid":2066581,"uid":194203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43961d6900b0e73b15d9e8310b9985b91e0230ec","tid":2066581,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:17:16.000Z","msg":"Gay<br />\n男人先會叫自己小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/d